{"tid":412220,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日晚餐","createTime":"2017-09-24T12:56:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T13:52:44.000Z","uid":59664,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe0d478de01bbd4fa2efb654222d971870592dc","tid":412220,"uid":59664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:56:26.000Z","msg":"又是拌飯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/205523_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F205523_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3e6354ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個底係薯蓉溝肉碎<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/205017_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F205017_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=90c9ba8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後鋪層飯<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/205231_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F205231_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9a0e31e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鋪埋啲雞蛋絲,蘿蔔絲,牙菜,青瓜絲上去<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/205301_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F205301_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e5264c68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/205358_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F205358_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6805dd50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後加埋豬肉絲, 淋啲芝麻醬,辣椒醬同埋辣油<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/24/205500_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F24%2F205500_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=4428ec92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n撈埋一齊就搞掂<br />\n20蚊都唔洗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c32b5e3eed948bde0e091d248fb304abdd37b84","tid":412220,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c930cbc142eb8f022e1dc59cba7517a0d7c496","tid":412220,"uid":59664,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n望落似狗糧但好好味"},{"pid":"d61330367ea56425b66167e2a4753338e9d9fcdd","tid":412220,"uid":66099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd9c5c0cd4202fe3d2f7a885f86d0a60032e7f2","tid":412220,"uid":59664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:59:30.000Z","msg":"做完尖食無得頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609af9d4c008362a4d85acd07105271521066973","tid":412220,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:00:24.000Z","msg":"好正咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eedf9d821e9197812bfce23e7d23a368511cc45","tid":412220,"uid":59664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:02:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好正咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></block